                <li><strong>Financial Data:</strong> Financial information, such as data related to your payment method (e.g., valid credit card number, card brand, expiration date).</li>
                <li><strong>Transaction Data:</strong> Details about purchases you make through the Site, including purchase amount, date, and payment method.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>How We Collect Your Information</h3>
            <p>We collect information about you through:</p>
            <ul>
