                <li><strong>Automated Technologies:</strong> Through cookies, web server logs, and other similar technologies.</li>
                <li><strong>Third Parties:</strong> From service providers that perform services on our behalf.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
